data.description: Sellers will accept or counter offers between $270-$290k.Great Eastside Location, and nestled in a quiet and sought-after neighborhood, with no HOA! Charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home. Updated kitchen with large island, custom backsplash, modern gray  cabinets and breakfast bar. Spacious family room off the kitchen with double doors that lead out to the patio. Enjoy the  huge backyard with an extra covered patio, 2 sheds, new corrugated metal fence and small grass area. A balance of peaceful living and easy access to nearby amenities. Come take a view!
